{
  "stem": "24515.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I can show you, I think, the documents that they sent my father, to first stop his being a notary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In Germany, when you were a lawyer for a certain time and had a certain reputation, you were given the Office of Notary, which was a bit more than what we do here.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But that was taken away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then he was not permitted to represent any Aryans, any Germans, only Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then he was-- that was taken away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was-- he had no more-- no more livelihood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "While he was defending Jews, the story I get is that you know, some Jew had been caught trying to smuggle some money across a border on which the Nazis had put the death penalty.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was in big trouble.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, would this lawyer defend him?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, no, I couldn't possibly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's got a wife and children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He can't to take the chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he says, why don't you go see Hartmann?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He may be crazy enough to take your case.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Hartmann, invariably, was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And had some successes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's a story that in one-- in one case, during the-- during the break in the case, he turned to the journalists.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And said well, gentlemen, of course we are quite-- we quite understand that if my client were not a Jew, he would have been released, freed, long ago.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when the judge came back, the man was freed within minutes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Another time, the prosecutor made a passionate speech about these dastardly Jews doing this, that, and the other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know-- you know, it was this terrible crook.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a sharpening condition-- what's the term-- not extenuating circumstances.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What is a circumstance that makes it worse?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Extenuating?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, extenuating makes it better.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
